sql: SELECT COUNT(address_id), address_details FROM Addresses WHERE address_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND EXISTS (SELECT * FROM Delivery_Route_Locations AS c WHERE Addresses.address_id = c.location_address_id) ORDER BY address_details DESC
SELECT l.actual_order_id, l.product_id FROM Actual_Order_Products AS l WHERE  l.actual_order_id >= 56 GROUP BY l.product_id
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT k.actual_order_id), COUNT(DISTINCT k.product_id), k.product_id FROM Actual_Order_Products AS k WHERE  k.actual_order_id = 65 ORDER BY k.product_id DESC
SELECT address_id, zip_postcode, city FROM Addresses WHERE  address_id > 74 GROUP BY city HAVING MIN(address_id) < 89 LIMIT 6

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT actual_order_id), Products.product_id FROM Regular_Order_Products JOIN Actual_Order_Products JOIN Regular_Orders JOIN Products ON Regular_Order_Products.regular_order_id = Regular_Orders.regular_order_id AND Products.product_id = Regular_Order_Products.product_id AND Actual_Order_Products.product_id = Products.product_id WHERE Regular_Order_Products.regular_order_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND  actual_order_id = 96 LIMIT 1
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT regular_order_id), COUNT(DISTINCT distributer_id), regular_order_id FROM Regular_Orders WHERE  regular_order_id > 51
SELECT route_name, other_route_details FROM Delivery_Routes GROUP BY route_name
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT product_name), product_name, product_description FROM Products WHERE  product_price <= 69 GROUP BY product_description HAVING SUM(product_price) < 35 LIMIT 3
SELECT COUNT(location_address_id), route_id FROM Delivery_Route_Locations WHERE  location_address_id = 20 ORDER BY route_id ASC LIMIT 4
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT product_id) FROM Actual_Order_Products WHERE  actual_order_id = 40
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT truck_details), COUNT(DISTINCT truck_licence_number), truck_licence_number FROM Trucks WHERE  truck_id = 71 ORDER BY truck_licence_number ASC
SELECT k.product_id FROM Actual_Order_Products AS k WHERE  k.actual_order_id = 100 GROUP BY k.product_id ORDER BY k.product_id DESC
SELECT MAX(truck_id), truck_id FROM Trucks WHERE  truck_id > 9

SELECT Actual_Order_Products.product_id, product_price FROM Regular_Order_Products JOIN Actual_Order_Products JOIN Products ON Products.product_id = Regular_Order_Products.product_id AND Actual_Order_Products.product_id = Products.product_id WHERE  Actual_Order_Products.product_id > 31 GROUP BY Actual_Order_Products.product_id HAVING SUM(Actual_Order_Products.product_id) > 3 ORDER BY Actual_Order_Products.product_id DESC LIMIT 9

SELECT MAX(employee_id), location_code FROM Trucks JOIN Order_Deliveries JOIN Employees ON Order_Deliveries.driver_employee_id = Employees.employee_id AND Trucks.truck_id = Order_Deliveries.truck_id WHERE truck_details = (SELECT MAX(truck_details) FROM Trucks AS v)
SELECT order_status_code FROM Actual_Orders JOIN Regular_Orders ON Regular_Orders.regular_order_id = Actual_Orders.regular_order_id WHERE  Actual_Orders.regular_order_id != 84

SELECT COUNT(Products.product_id), AVG(actual_order_id), COUNT(DISTINCT actual_order_id), product_price FROM Actual_Order_Products JOIN Products ON Actual_Order_Products.product_id = Products.product_id WHERE product_price BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND product_price IN (SELECT product_price FROM Products AS d WHERE d.product_price BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND  d.product_price < 93 LIMIT 8) GROUP BY product_price HAVING MIN(product_price) <= 56 ORDER BY product_price DESC
SELECT address_type, customer_name FROM Customer_Addresses JOIN Customers ON Customers.customer_id = Customer_Addresses.customer_id WHERE  Customer_Addresses.customer_id = 36 GROUP BY customer_name

SELECT Regular_Order_Products.regular_order_id, order_status_code FROM Regular_Order_Products JOIN Customers JOIN Actual_Orders JOIN Regular_Orders ON Regular_Orders.distributer_id = Customers.customer_id AND Regular_Orders.regular_order_id = Actual_Orders.regular_order_id AND Regular_Order_Products.regular_order_id = Regular_Orders.regular_order_id WHERE  Regular_Orders.regular_order_id <= 22
SELECT y.address_id FROM Addresses AS y WHERE  y.address_id > 33 LIMIT 2

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT order_status_code), order_status_code FROM Actual_Order_Products JOIN Actual_Orders ON Actual_Orders.actual_order_id = Actual_Order_Products.actual_order_id WHERE product_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND actual_order_date NOT IN (SELECT actual_order_date FROM Actual_Orders WHERE  regular_order_id = 22) LIMIT 5

SELECT w.regular_order_id FROM Actual_Orders AS w WHERE  w.actual_order_id != 72 OR order_status_code IN (SELECT order_status_code FROM Actual_Orders AS e WHERE  e.regular_order_id <= 44 LIMIT 3) ORDER BY w.regular_order_id DESC

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT location_name), location_code FROM Delivery_Route_Locations WHERE route_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR route_id IN (SELECT route_id FROM Delivery_Routes AS v) ORDER BY location_code DESC
SELECT distributer_id FROM Regular_Orders WHERE distributer_id IN (SELECT distributer_id FROM Regular_Orders WHERE  regular_order_id = 34) ORDER BY distributer_id DESC
SELECT actual_order_id FROM Delivery_Route_Locations JOIN Order_Deliveries ON Delivery_Route_Locations.location_code = Order_Deliveries.location_code WHERE  driver_employee_id <= 68 LIMIT 10

SELECT MIN(driver_employee_id), employee_phone FROM Order_Deliveries JOIN Employees ON Order_Deliveries.driver_employee_id = Employees.employee_id WHERE delivery_date > (SELECT AVG(delivery_date) FROM Order_Deliveries WHERE actual_order_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10) ORDER BY employee_phone ASC

SELECT Actual_Order_Products.actual_order_id, order_status_code FROM Actual_Order_Products JOIN Actual_Orders ON Actual_Orders.actual_order_id = Actual_Order_Products.actual_order_id WHERE  Actual_Orders.actual_order_id != 80 ORDER BY Actual_Order_Products.actual_order_id ASC LIMIT 4

SELECT product_name FROM Actual_Order_Products JOIN Products ON Actual_Order_Products.product_id = Products.product_id WHERE EXISTS (SELECT * FROM Actual_Order_Products WHERE  actual_order_id = 73 AND Products.product_id = product_id) ORDER BY product_name ASC
